%5 => Enemy_Charge 
%4 => Enemy_Suffocate
%4 => Enemy_Attack_Wall
%3 => Enemy_Grab_Ground
%3 => Enemy_Throw
%1 => Enemy_Steal

=>< Resolve_HP
=> END

~ Enemy_Charge 
Charge and tackle

=> END

~ Enemy_Suffocate
Enemy Trying to suffocate you
=> END

~ Enemy_Attack_Wall
Enemy try to push to to the wall and beat you
=> END

~ Enemy_Grab_Ground
Enemy Grab and 
=> END

~ Enemy_Throw
Enemy Throw a chair
=> END

~ Enemy_Steal
Enemy Steal
=> END